Monthly in-person event


Science Café


A space where curious people come together to talk about science. No lectures, no slides — just a great topic and a room full of people who want to understand the world better.





&lt;div class="sc-label"&gt;Next event&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="sc-cafe-card" style="max-width:700px;"&gt;
  &lt;div class="sc-cafe-date"&gt;
