  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-cafe-title"&gt;Is AI making us worse at thinking?&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-cafe-detail"&gt;📍 The Common Room, 14 Broad Street · 7:00–9:00 pm&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-cafe-detail"&gt;🎟 Free admission · All welcome&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-cafe-desc"&gt;From GPS eroding our sense of direction to autocomplete finishing our sentences, we've been offloading cognitive tasks to machines for decades. Come with your opinions, your doubts, and your questions.&lt;/div&gt;
