&lt;div class="sc-label"&gt;How it works&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="sc-steps"&gt;
  &lt;div class="sc-step"&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-step-num"&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-step-text"&gt;
      &lt;strong&gt;We pick a topic&lt;/strong&gt;
      Topics come from our community — science in the news, emerging research, or a big question someone's been mulling. Announced two weeks before each event.
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="sc-step"&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-step-num"&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-step-text"&gt;
      &lt;strong&gt;We gather and talk&lt;/strong&gt;
      Doors open at 6:30 pm, discussion starts at 7 pm. A facilitator guides the conversation — no experts, no panels, no wrong answers. Everyone participates.
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="sc-step"&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-step-num"&gt;3&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-step-text"&gt;
      &lt;strong&gt;We share a recap&lt;/strong&gt;
      After each event, a short summary goes on the blog. Some discussions become podcast episodes.
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="sc-step"&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-step-num"&gt;4&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="sc-step-text"&gt;
      &lt;strong&gt;You suggest the next topic&lt;/strong&gt;
      At the end of every Café, we vote on future topics. Your idea might be next.
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;





